Acceptance Criteria:
AC:
- PATCH /api/projects/{id}/health accepts {health_status: 'red'|'amber'|'green', health_notes?: string}
- Auth: pm, leadership, admin
- Writes health_status to projects table
- health_notes stored in weekly_status_logs as a new log entry with topics_covered='Health update: [health_notes]' when provided
- GET /api/reporting/summary response includes projects_by_health: {red: number, amber: number, green: number}
- Governance event emitted: {update_text: 'health_status updated to [value]', type: 'micro'}
- Returns 400 for invalid enum value
